prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and funny watercolor greeting card. A charming cartoon pig, wearing a jaunty little party hat slightly askew on its head, is gleefully leaping into a giant, messy chocolate birthday cake. Splatters of chocolate frosting and colorful sprinkles fly through the air in an artistic, joyful explosion. The pig has a look of pure, unadulterated bliss on its face. The background is a soft wash of pastel watercolor, with confetti gently floating down. The entire scene is painted in a vibrant, flowing watercolor style with soft edges and beautiful color bleeds. In the center, in a beautiful, readable, elegant cursive script, the words "Go hog wild, it's your birthday!" are written. Flat 2D artwork, perfect for printing.
